@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api
@token = COLE_O_TOKEN_AQUI
@refreshToken = COLE_O_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Descoberta da API
GET {{apiUrl}}

### Registrar usuario
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Usuario Teste",
  "usuario": "teste_api",
  "senha": "Senha@12345"
}

### Login (copie o token da resposta para a variavel @token)
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuario": "teste_api",
  "senha": "Senha@12345"
}

### Refresh de sessao
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Listar salas (protegido)
GET {{apiUrl}}/salas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar alunos da sala 1 (protegido)
GET {{apiUrl}}/salas/1/alunos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Salvar frequencia da sala 1 (protegido)
POST {{apiUrl}}/frequencia
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "salaId": 1,
  "data": "2026-03-21",
  "registros": [
    { "alunoId": 1, "status": "presente" },
    { "alunoId": 2, "status": "falta" },
    { "alunoId": 3, "status": "presente" }
  ]
}

### Consultar frequencia da sala 1 em uma data (protegido)
GET {{apiUrl}}/frequencia/sala/1/data/2026-03-21
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Historico da sala 1 (protegido)
GET {{apiUrl}}/frequencia/sala/1/historico?inicio=2026-03-01&fim=2026-03-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar alunos para cadastro de responsavel (protegido)
GET {{apiUrl}}/responsaveis/alunos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cadastrar responsavel (protegido)
POST {{apiUrl}}/responsaveis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nomeResponsavel": "Maria Oliveira",
  "email": "maria.oliveira@example.com",
  "nomeAluno": "Ana Clara",
  "telefone": "(11)99999-9999"
}

### Listar responsaveis de um aluno (protegido)
GET {{apiUrl}}/responsaveis/aluno/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Logout
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
